{"tid":409610,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【iPhone 8】記錯零售價以為先達有平貨執　白衫男高興5分鐘","createTime":"2017-09-22T08:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T06:17:57.000Z","uid":51904,"like":314,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0b6ddf87af782745ee05513c7819ee557b2988","tid":409610,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"以往蘋果店有新電話登場，先達均有大批「果農」等待出售手機，惟下月有記念版的iPhoneX登場，加上貨源充足，今日先達的「炒情」慘淡。<br />\n<br />\n十一時許來到先達廣場的譚先生，看見有手機店的金色 256GB iPhone8售價為8,200元，由於他誤以為官方零售價為8288元，於是爽快地交易，以為從中「賺」了88元，更即場露出勝利者的笑容：「上網睇資料，知道無得炒價，原本想買上台機，但先來博一博，所以有心理準備。」惟5分鐘後，譚才發現手機原價為8,188元，即要「倒蝕」12元才買到新機。但他強調自己並非炒家，即使買貴12元也未有失望，並即場入卡使用，指仍會「開心換新機」。<br />\n<br />\n先達數碼店員連小姐表示，今早開場已不見以往人山人海的「畫面」，該店亦未有人客前來「放機」，場面顯得冷清：「你睇入嚟放機愁眉苦臉，我宜家都愁眉苦臉呀。」"},{"pid":"5b6b37fa2a9e36d9d51c8a5fab532dc0d05f5b9a","tid":409610,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de3a30fa10b66cd2ac4bd003ba1b5ddbacae7ea","tid":409610,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:15:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca910a6472c77587bb85ff0251c56b36aa8e4b65","tid":409610,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a0fd5108f49a6a53be06305d8d5f91458e4890","tid":409610,"uid":68094,"like":189,"dislike":0,"score":189,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a1f46005de5638c51d7d105546ac76ab21d407e","tid":409610,"uid":26419,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:21:2